content:
cfallin opened PR #4796 from aarch64-isle-misc to main:

  • get_pinned_reg / set_pinned_reg
  • bitcast
  • stack_addr
  • extractlane
  • insertlane
  • vhigh_bits
  • iadd_ifcout
  • fcvt_low_from_sint

After this PR and the load/store porting in #4785, we have only tls_value and flag-dependent ops remaining.
